    • asHttpStream

    • notHandled

      protected void notHandled()
      Creating a StatisticsHandler.StatisticsRequest increments the request counter before its gets a chance of figuring out if the request is going to be handled by the wrapped handler. In case the wrapped handler did not handle the request, calling this method decrements the request counter to compensate for the unneeded increment.
